overview:
Kattelo is a consulting firm headquartered in San Francisco, California. The primary objective is to help clients leverage technologies to enhance productivity.

Kattelo design and create software solutions that accomplish complicated tasks in a simple and effective way. Kattelo’s specialty is the development of sophisticated back-office web applications using Microsoft SharePoint and .NET platforms.
